      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "## How to Play Early Game\n**Aggressive:**\n- Drop at a Named Location\n- Try and aim to wipe out most people at your dropspot to accumulate kills quickly\n- Get good fighting loot and get good mats.\n- Look for quick kills and aim to end fights early and efficiently.\n\n\n**Passive:**\n- Drop at a unnamed location or passive POI\n- Loot up as efficiently as possible and aim to get max mats\n- Try and rotate by following people and go through the side of storm circles by aiming to get a deadside position\n- If you want surge damage look for teams rotating late into zone, as long as you dont take much damage during offspawn you wont need much\n\n## How to Rotate Early Game\n- Follow a loot path to ensure you finish looting before other players do.\n- Rotate deadside to avoid other players\n- Be quick, If that means missing out on a bit of loot thats ok, storm is extreamly fast this season without a lot of movement\n- HEAVILY prioritise getting a medium to high priority position on the map as early as you can",
